n","original_language":"en"},{"id":425505,"adult":false,"title":"Kin","video":false,"overview":"A young boy finds a powerful otherworldly weapon, which he uses to save his older adoptive brother from a crew of thugs. Before long, the two of them are also pursued by federal agents and mysterious mercenaries aiming to reclaim their asset.","genre_ids":[878,28,12,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":2.4008,"vote_count":872,"poster_path":"/oPE5GXHaTlu5eRcd4USuOX3A1mf.jpg","release_date":"2018-08-29","vote_average":6.1,"backdrop_path":"/7oZR0oaFOPrzGkg3ZntEKwMCLTe.jpg","original_title":"Kin","original_language":"en"},{"id":335797,"adult":false,"title":"Sing","video":false,"overview":"A koala named Buster recruits his best friend to help him drum up business for his theater by hosting a singing competition.","genre_ids":[10751,35,10402,16],"media_type":"movie","popularity":6.8047,"vote_count":8334,"poster_path":"/b8UiFXwMrSXVTHM0fb2twl8uE8a.jpg","release_date":"2016-11-23","vote_average":7.1,"backdrop_path":"/z9ft5HYHzWcasR6SGcgeluxTznB.jpg","original_title":"Sing","original_language":"en"},{"id":333484,"adult":false,"title":"The Magnificent Seven","video":false,"overview":"Looking to mine for gold, greedy industrialist Bartholomew Bogue seizes control of the Old West town of Rose Creek. With their lives in jeopardy, Emma Cullen and other desperate residents turn to bounty hunter Sam Chisolm for help. Chisolm recruits an eclectic group of gunslingers to take on Bogue and his ruthless henchmen. With a deadly showdown on the horizon, the seven mercenaries soon find themselves fighting for more than just money once the bullets start to fly.","genre_ids":[12,28,37],"media_type":"movie","popularity":4.7216,"vote_count":6283,"poster_path":"/ezcS78TIjgr85pVdaPDd2rSPVNs.jpg","release_date":"2016-09-14","vote_average":6.481,"backdrop_path":"/4qxZJRYe4ezA5J1sidnV7vuaYaz.jpg","original_title":"The Magnificent Seven","original_language":"en"}],"similar_content":[{"id":38,"adult":false,"title":"Eternal Sunshine of the Spotless Mind","video":false,"overview":"Joel Barish, heartbroken that his girlfriend underwent a procedure to erase him from her memory, decides to do the same. However, as he watches his memories of her fade away, he realises that he still loves her, and may be too late to correct his mistake.","genre_ids":[878,18,10749],"popularity":10.9255,"vote_count":16054,"poster_path":"/5MwkWH9tYHv3mV9OdYTMR5qreIz.jpg","release_date":"2004-03-19","vote_average":8.091,"backdrop_path":"/jzZcW65MZQfAgvbEoX8EWCvlxpk.jpg","original_title":"Eternal Sunshine of the Spotless Mind","original_language":"en"},{"id":66,"adult":false,"title":"Absolute Power","video":false,"overview":"A master thief coincidentally is robbing a house where a murder—in which the President of the United States is involved—occurs in front of his eyes. He is forced to run, while holding evidence that could convict the President.","genre_ids":[80,18,28],"popularity":2.9898,"vote_count":1203,"poster_path":"/izvyt3cxlilhbYwybTOteDWqf99.jpg","release_date":"1997-02-14","vote_average":6.658,"backdrop_path":"/cLftTzGw40BlLw8IggKSWDjKOQo.jpg","original_title":"Absolute Power","original_language":"en"},{"id":3132,"adult":false,"title":"Bad Company","video":false,"overview":"When a Harvard-educated CIA agent is killed during an operation, the secret agency recruits his twin brother.","genre_ids":[28,12,35,53],"popularity":1.7734,"vote_count":845,"poster_path":"/umu141mcfIEhRLgyQp7TWlGJFW.jpg","release_date":"2002-06-07","vote_average":5.513,"backdrop_path":"/9oLrsekWm3sfEGw5HOav6roW1h7.jpg","original_title":"Bad Company","original_language":"en"},{"id":6637,"adult":false,"title":"National Treasure: Book of Secrets","video":false,"overview":"Benjamin Franklin Gates and Abigail Chase re-team with Riley Poole and, now armed with a stack of long-lost pages from John Wilkes Booth's diary, Ben must follow a clue left there to prove his ancestor's innocence in the assassination of Abraham Lincoln.","genre_ids":[28,12,9648,53],"popularity":5.7661,"vote_count":5448,"poster_path":"/dc9F1vNOGbgeZrO9ejNkbgHPlfw.jpg","release_date":"2007-12-19","vote_average":6.371,"backdrop_path":"/oESkLej3EmCMs8mprWf73TUOdsu.jpg","original_title":"National Treasure: Book of Secrets","original_language":"en"},{"id":6696,"adult":false,"title":"UFOria","video":false,"overview":"Sheldon Bart (Fred Ward) is a drifter, and a small-time con man. He meets his old friend, Brother Bud (Harry Dean Stanton), a big-time con man into faith healing and fencing stolen cars, at his revival tent outside a small town. While he's helping Brother Bud, he falls in love with Arlene (Cindy Williams), a local supermarket clerk who believes in UFOs and is deeply religious and deeply lonely. When Arlene has a vision of a coming UFO, everyone deals with it in their own way.","genre_ids":[35,878],"popularity":2.7568,"vote_count":9,"poster_path":"/jYz4qNacamBEiZJTmGtxaHigGjn.jpg","release_date":"1984-07-10","vote_average":5.6,"backdrop_path":"/z884s7ER2olQrbI9uHpv9Yvl44p.jpg","original_title":"UFOria","original_language":"en"},{"id":6883,"adult":false,"title":"Two-Minute Warning","video":false,"overview":"A psychotic sniper plans a massive killing spree in a Los Angeles football stadium during a major championship game. The police, led by Captain Peter Holly and the SWAT commander, learn of the plot and rush to the scene.","genre_ids":[28,53],"popularity":0.9261,"vote_count":94,"poster_path":"/qrQ6Y0kWmW89jvWy6I58PsbGZen.jpg","release_date":"1976-11-12","vote_average":6.2,"backdrop_path":"/dUttBVsFoZCZaSKuFNK8wcyjf85.jpg","original_title":"Two-Minute Warning","original_language":"en"},{"id":6916,"adult":false,"title":"Watch Out, We're Mad","video":false,"overview":"After a tied 1st place in a local stunt race, two drivers start a contest to decide who of them will own the prize, a dune buggy. But when a mobster destroys the car, they are determined to get it back.","genre_ids":[28,35],"popularity":1.8