lt":false,"title":"The Mummy","video":false,"overview":"Dashing legionnaire Rick O'Connell stumbles upon the hidden ruins of Hamunaptra while in the midst of a battle to claim the area in 1920s Egypt. It has been over three thousand years since former High Priest Imhotep suffered a fate worse than death as a punishment for a forbidden love—along with a curse that guarantees eternal doom upon the world if he is ever awoken.","genre_ids":[12,28,14],"popularity":16.3858,"vote_count":9783,"poster_path":"/yhIsVvcUm7QxzLfT6HW2wLf5ajY.jpg","release_date":"1999-04-16","vote_average":6.962,"backdrop_path":"/8zLS8p1tRyWFLRFfmgQq0j5WE6z.jpg","original_title":"The Mummy","original_language":"en"},{"id":271825,"adult":false,"title":"Billa","video":false,"overview":"Billa, a powerful outlaw with a long list of enemies, kills Rajesh, a member of his gang, after he quits the criminal life. But Rajesh's fiancee and his sister pledge to take revenge on Billa.","genre_ids":[28,80,53],"popularity":0.8138,"vote_count":10,"poster_path":"/cjEGhN4w6pnsi2z4mgmMvdMYyub.jpg","release_date":"1980-01-26","vote_average":7,"backdrop_path":"/w4OAgU0jvnJ6DqDK2LPtwwgICr8.jpg","original_title":"பில்லா","original_language":"ta"},{"id":271916,"adult":false,"title":"Uncharted: Eye of Indra","video":false,"overview":"In this motion comic set before the events shown of Uncharted: Drake's Fortune, Nathan Drake is hired by the sinister Daniel Pinkerton to track down a treasure called the Eye of Indra.","genre_ids":[28,12,16],"popularity":0.254,"vote_count":8,"poster_path":"/kw03vncbtgjgx9OZqpSZzdtC4x1.jpg","release_date":"2009-10-22","vote_average":6.2,"backdrop_path":"/coYapkwiwWwachN36ZO3tjrBsa8.jpg","original_title":"Uncharted: Eye of Indra","original_language":"en"},{"id":274855,"adult":false,"title":"Geostorm","video":false,"overview":"After an unprecedented series of natural disasters threatened the planet, the world's leaders came together to create an intricate network of satellites to control the global climate and keep everyone safe. But now, something has gone wrong: the system built to protect Earth is attacking it, and it becomes a race against the clock to uncover the real threat before a worldwide geostorm wipes out everything and everyone along with it.","genre_ids":[28,878,53],"popularity":6.8076,"vote_count":5072,"poster_path":"/nrsx0jEaBgXq4PWo7SooSnYJTv.jpg","release_date":"2017-10-12","vote_average":6.111,"backdrop_path":"/vIEuJiIZN9EclAJDmD49F2zUzuX.jpg","original_title":"Geostorm","original_language":"en"},{"id":4349,"adult":false,"title":"The Kingdom","video":false,"overview":"A team of U.S. government agents is sent to investigate the bombing of an American facility in the Middle East.","genre_ids":[53,28,18],"popularity":3.4411,"vote_count":1775,"poster_path":"/8CSiRnMRLuKT58JiOGzQ7p1oa1b.jpg","release_date":"2007-08-22","vote_average":6.727,"backdrop_path":"/qzmCz3tK2v5BFLQYgbQVGmTI3YD.jpg","original_title":"The Kingdom","original_language":"en"},{"id":4141,"adult":false,"title":"Shoot 'Em Up","video":false,"overview":"A man named Mr. Smith delivers a woman's baby during a shootout, and is then called upon to protect the newborn from the army of gunmen.","genre_ids":[28,53,35,80],"popularity":2.6924,"vote_count":2016,"poster_path":"/hZ4p0MvSUWnCCL0IUn47UXTVPCs.jpg","release_date":"2007-07-26","vote_average":6.478,"backdrop_path":"/1bYY2WUsHyCl66gQAGoF40JIryW.jpg","original_title":"Shoot 'Em Up","original_language":"en"},{"id":468219,"adult":false,"title":"Dead in a Week (Or Your Money Back)","video":false,"overview":"William has failed to kill himself so many times that he outsources his suicide to aging assassin Leslie. But with the contract signed and death assured within a week (or his money back), William suddenly discovers reasons to live... However Leslie is under pressure from his boss to make sure the contract is completed.","genre_ids":[35,28,18],"popularity":1.1576,"vote_count":361,"poster_path":"/f4ANVEuEaGy2oP5M0Y2P1dwxUNn.jpg","